            "h1": "sectionTitle",
            "text": "UI-DESIGN & OTHER"
          },
          {
            "p": "sectionText",
            "text": "My interest in user interface design comes from my personal passion for art and design."
          },
          {
            "p": "sectionText",
            "text": "Often, a client who wants to create a website expects comprehensive work, not only to design what the website should contain, but also to design the user's interface."
          },
          {
            "p": "sectionText",
            "text": "Knowledge of such tools as Gimp, Inkscape and Figma allow to realize these expectations."
          },
          {
            "p": "sectionText",
            "text": "Below I present selected projects, such as: UI of websites, icons and logos, graphic design (eg. book covers, infographics) as well as my art activities (paintings and drawings)."
          }
        ]
