            "p": "sectionText",
            "text": "My interest in applied graphics results from my artistic activity, which I have been running since my youth."
          },
          {
            "p": "sectionText",
            "text": "I mainly do acrylic painting, but also drawing. I had several individual exhibitions, mainly in Elblag, where I come from (e.g. in custody), as well as collective exhibitions (e.g. in Duseldorf in 2009, at Galeria El - 'Salon Elbląski' in 2009, 2011, 2013)."
          },
          {
            "p": "sectionText",
            "text": "I was also a co-founder of Klaster Biznesu Kultury 'BizArt' (Business of Culture Cluster), which was established on May 11, 2011 in Elbląg."
